pull_request.title: Admin Panel - Banners and Favorites Bugfix
pull_request.body:
# Admin Notifications & Color Enhancements

## Overview
This PR implements an admin notification banner system and fixes UI issues with the favorites page. It also improves the color theming across the application to better match our coffee aesthetic.

## Changes

### Admin Notifications System (Closes #8)
The new banner system provides flexible, dismissible notifications for administrators to communicate with users.

#### Database Changes
```prisma
model AdminBanner {
  id            String   @id @default(cuid())
  title         String
  description   String
  color         BannerColor @default(neutral)
  isActive      Boolean  @default(true)
  isDismissable Boolean  @default(true)
  createdAt     DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt     DateTime @updatedAt
  dismissals    UserDismissedBanner[]
}

enum BannerColor {
  success
  info
  danger
  warning
  neutral
}
```

#### UI Components
The [`AdminBanner`](src/app/components/AdminBanner.tsx) component now supports:
- Multiple banner colors with semantic meanings
- Customizable opacity levels
- Dismissal functionality with persistence
- Responsive design

```tsx
const colorMap = {
  success: "bg-success/20 text-success border-success/30",
  info: "bg-info/20 text-info border-info/30",
  danger: "bg-error/20 text-error border-error/30",
  warning: "bg-warning/20 text-warning border-warning/30",
  neutral: "bg-base-content/20 text-base-content border-base-content/30",
};
```

#### Color System Updates
Enhanced the semantic colors to be richer and more coffee-themed:

```css
/* Coffee-themed semantic colors */
--color-error: oklch(50% 0.25 25);    /* rich red */
--color-warning: oklch(60% 0.15 80);  /* rich caramel */
--color-info: oklch(45% 0.15 220);    /* deep water blue */
--color-success: oklch(45% 0.15 140); /* deep forest green */
```

### Favorites Page Bug Fix (Fixes #55)
- Fixed data refresh issues when locations change
- Added proper error handling and loading states
- Improved UI feedback during data loading

```tsx
const handleLocationUpdate = async () => {
  try {
    const response = await fetch(`/api/user/favorites`);
    if (response.ok) {
      const data = await response.json();
      setFavorites(data);
    }
  } catch (err) {
    console.error("Error refreshing favorites:", err);
  }
};
```

## Implementation Details
1. Added banner system to key pages:
   - Login/Register
   - Dashboard
   - Main app layout
2. Implemented banner persistence with dismissal tracking
3. Enhanced color system for better accessibility
4. Fixed favorites page data synchronization

## Migration Steps
```bash
# Deploy the new banner system migration
npx prisma migrate deploy

# Verify the migration
npx prisma generate
```

## Testing Checklist
- [ ] Banner displays correctly in all color variants
- [ ] Banner dismissal persists across sessions
- [ ] Favorites update correctly after location changes
- [ ] Color contrast meets accessibility standards

# Screenshots
![Screenshot 2025-05-11 at 7 36 03 PM](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/160c88b4-fb53-4b49-bd93-dbb2c869bc84)
